  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decision and Strategy</h2>Each turn, decide whether to acquire new units, expand the map, or obtain new beneficial effects. Arrange units in a way that maximizes benefits for each unit without causing negative impacts on others.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roguelite Elements</h2>There are four main types of units: dwarves, devices, plants, and animals. Each unit has its unique characteristics and production impact. At higher difficulties, disaster units may appear, which create avoidable negative effects.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/3423d71ef4be85fee0930c8bd0fffa91.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/118e4492f1f2c2dd7db3dc9516d0f74f.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/02127cd814786935426ca12a71ea3e3f.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/13efc1084a1118d9c325e74abe889ddf.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br>Different buffs: These special global buffs provide a large amount of coins. Choose different units based on the selected buffs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/71086490facaf72985e1a2bcb8f19fde.avif?t=1723621857\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105690/extras/29787841e023c3b4e530cf423c8f0869.avif?t=1723621857\" wi